{"tid":1611253,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"終極和理非其實可以做多步","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:31:23.000Z","uid":310371,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7087fcf5c0c2fed4d745b2ec228449cd9a3ae8cb","tid":1611253,"uid":310371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實好多人都有開po講過, 但係冇人理，哨兵好緊要<br />\n行完不反之後， 唔好淨係返屋企睇直播，唔該去 遊行地點附近做哨兵， 驚嘅咪返自己屋企嗰區守係唔同路口睇下狗車行到邊/睇下巴士站有冇狗<br />\n依家淨係知狗向緊邊一個方向走， 唔知道行到去邊 ，仲有幾耐到，仲有幾耐會同前線接觸。<br />\n要走，點走？ 好多人轉車嗰時畀人拉<br />\n<br />\n依家好多時哨兵係前線做埋， 變咗前線視野好細， 好容易畀狗伏<br />\n<br />\n一份詳細啲嘅地圖 可以幫到前線做好啲嘅決定<br />\n<br />\n前線同你打生打死， 做多一步畀張好啲嘅地圖人哋都得啩， 企喺度影兩張相唔犯法㗎<br />\n<br />\nTLDR  和理非行完不反後請去做哨兵"},{"pid":"1a814be23d0eaf6fd60050be26f4a0bc8ea61cdd","tid":1611253,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:08:33.000Z","msg":"今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2omJSt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2omJSt.jpg&h=720cd796&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ln9X1D9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLn9X1D9.jpg&h=1fd7c745&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHTh1D9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHTh1D9.jpg&h=f1e9f20f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1bc78b9fe44b27e6dc0d7d947096ce5fc33a326","tid":1611253,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:09:28.000Z","msg":"而家香港係一個誰大誰惡誰正確既時代<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64091d0d2b00c3e59330995f35e06dfbdf24fa33","tid":1611253,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"銀髮軍師 <span style=